<plot>Based on the true life story of the director Michael Grais. The film follows the rocky and dramatic relationship between a husband and wife and how that effects their children and specifically their sons relationships with women. Set in the early 1960's and filmed in black and white, the film does a beautiful job of capturing the glamor of the era with the chaos of the family.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?318350</url></doc>
